      <p data-lang-en style="display:none">
        Currency exchange rates displayed on this site are sourced from a third-party API (frankfurter.app) and may differ from actual bank or market rates. These rates are for informational purposes only. Always verify rates with your bank or exchange provider before making real financial transactions.
